</Output>
</Group><Text-field style="Normal" layout="Normal">We see that <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display=""></Equation>, and that this is the first number greater than 0.99.
</Text-field><Text-field style="Normal" layout="Normal">Here is a slicker way:</Text-field>
